### PHASE 1.3: SLEEP DEEP DIVE (Неделя 5-6)

#### Database Schema Extensions
```sql
sleep_sessions
├── id (uuid)
├── user_id (uuid)
├── date (date)
├── bedtime (timestamp)
├── wake_time (timestamp)
├── duration_minutes (int)
├── sleep_latency_minutes (int) -- time to fall asleep
├── awake_duration_minutes (int)
├── sleep_efficiency_percent (decimal 5,2)
├── source (enum: manual, wearable, phone_app)
├── quality_score (int 0-100)
└── notes (text)

sleep_phases
├── id (uuid)
├── sleep_session_id (uuid)
├── phase_type (enum: deep, light, rem, awake)
├── start_time (timestamp)
├── end_time (timestamp)
├── duration_minutes (int)
└── percentage_of_total (decimal 5,2)

sleep_metrics
├── id (uuid)
├── sleep_session_id (uuid)
├── heart_rate_avg (int)
├── hrv_avg (decimal 5,2)
├── breathing_rate_avg (decimal 4,1)
├── spo2_avg (decimal 4,1)
├── movement_score (int 0-100)
├── snoring_duration_minutes (int)
└── environmental_data (JSONB) -- temp, humidity, noise

sleep_goals
├── id (uuid)
├── user_id (uuid)
├── target_bedtime (time)
├── target_wake_time (time)
├── target_duration_minutes (int) -- 420-540 (7-9h)
├── chronotype (enum: lion, bear, wolf, dolphin)
├── is_smart_alarm_enabled (boolean)
├── smart_alarm_window_minutes (int) -- usually 30
└── is_active (boolean)

sleep_smart_alarms
├── id (uuid)
├── user_id (uuid)
├── sleep_session_id (uuid)
├── scheduled_time (timestamp)
├── actual_trigger_time (timestamp)
├── phase_at_trigger (enum: deep, light, rem, awake)
├── user_response (enum: dismissed, snoozed, missed)
└── effectiveness_rating (int 1-5)

sleep_routine_checklist
├── id (uuid)
├── user_id (uuid)
├── date (date)
├── pre_sleep_activities (JSONB)
│   ├── no_caffeine_after_14h (boolean)
│   ├── no_heavy_meal_3h_before (boolean)
│   ├── no_screens_1h_before (boolean)
│   ├── dimmed_lights (boolean)
│   ├── meditation_or_relaxation (boolean)
│   ├── consistent_bedtime (boolean)
│   └── cool_room (boolean)
└── environment_score (int 0-100)

sleep_factors
├── id (uuid)
├── sleep_session_id (uuid)
├── factor_type (enum: caffeine, alcohol, exercise, stress, medication, late_meal, nap)
├── factor_value (varchar 255)
├── estimated_impact (enum: positive, negative, neutral)
└── severity (int 1-10)

sleep_naps
├── id (uuid)
├── user_id (uuid)
├── start_time (timestamp)
├── end_time (timestamp)
├── duration_minutes (int)
├── nap_type (enum: power_nap_20min, restorative_90min)
├── quality_rating (int 1-5)
└── effect_on_night_sleep (enum: improved, no_effect, worsened)

sleep_weekly_summaries
├── id (uuid)
├── user_id (uuid)
├── week_start_date (date)
├── avg_duration_minutes (int)
├── avg_quality_score (int)
├── deep_sleep_avg_percent (decimal 5,2)
├── rem_sleep_avg_percent (decimal 5,2)
├── consistency_score (int 0-100)
└── sleep_debt_minutes (int)
