├── dosage_unit (varchar 20)
├── frequency (JSONB) -- complex scheduling
├── prescribed_by (varchar 255)
├── start_date (date)
├── end_date (date, nullable)
├── with_food (enum: before, with, after, empty_stomach)
├── reminder_enabled (boolean)
├── reminder_time (time[])
