├── scheduled_time (time)
├── location (varchar 255)
├── reason (text)
├── notes (text)
├── follow_up_needed (boolean)
├── follow_up_date (date)
└── status (enum: scheduled, completed, cancelled, no_show)

medicine_documents
├── id (uuid)
├── user_id (uuid)
├── document_type (enum: prescription, lab_result, discharge_summary, insurance, other)
